  <refnamediv>
    <refname>mtell</refname>
    <refpurpose> binary file management</refpurpose>
  </refnamediv>
  <refsynopsisdiv>
    <title>Calling Sequence</title>
    <synopsis>mtell([fd])</synopsis>
  </refsynopsisdiv>
  <refsection>
    <title>Arguments</title>
    <variablelist>
      <varlistentry>
        <term>fd</term>
        <listitem>
          <para>scalar. The <literal>fd</literal> parameter returned by the function <literal>mopen</literal>. -1 stands for last opened file. Default value is -1.</para>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>
    </variablelist>
  </refsection>
  <refsection>
    <title>Description</title>
    <para>
    The function <literal>mtell()</literal> returns the offset of the current byte  relative  to
    the beginning of the file associated with the named stream <literal>fd</literal>.</para>
  </refsection>
